text:
Sending unidentifiable agents to kidnap our neighbors and ordering Marines into our streets in the name of safe communities is disgusting. 

I spent decades as a community organizer in Oakland, I know what community safety looks like. This is not it. 

@POTUS, If you wanted safety you’d empower local law enforcement instead of sending in federal agents, you’d take guns off our streets, and you’d invest in programs that help people get and stay ahead.

I have family who have served abroad in the military. Our troops trust our government to have their backs, and we trust our government to keep the U.S. safe.

@SecDef and @MikeWaltz47’s mishandling and divulging of sensitive military information breaks that trust.

We must hold the Trump administration accountable.
